                                        206,
                                        1234,
                                        1190,
                                        2026
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " in a Manhattan world. We independently trained the VP estimator and distortion estimator using a minibatch size of 32. We optimized the VP estimator, which was pretrained on ImageNet [42], using the Adam optimizer [17] and Random Erasing augmentation [62] with "
                                },
