                                        1234,
                                        1190,
                                        2026
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " and was multiplied by 0.1 at the 100th epoch. We also trained the distortion estimator pretrained on Wakai et al.'s original network [53] using the RAdam optimizer [31] with a learning rate of "
