                                    "bbox": [
                                        206,
                                        2425,
                                        1190,
                                        2871
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "To demonstrate the validity and effectiveness of the proposed VP estimator, we used pose estimation metrics and the distance error between the detected and ground- truth VP/ADPs. Following [7], we used the standard keypoint metrics of the average precision (AP) and average recall (AR) [47] with a 5.6- pixel "
