                                        2970
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Overall, the VP estimator detected the VP/ADPs, although the performance in the cross- domain evaluation de "
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "bbox": [
                                1282,
                                1191,
